\s SHENGERO RY’IMANA IHORAHO
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Shengero ry’Imana Ihoraho, ntimuri ishengero nk’ayandi, ivyo ni mubimenye bagenzi, kuko muri ihanga riri ukwaryo; ihanga ry’Imana isumba vyose\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Umve rero ncuti zanje, dusang\bdit*\bdit iy’ukwizera kuzima, nimwihutire \bdit*\bdit kugendera mwese, mw’ijambo ry’Imana ryose, kuko niho hari ubugingo budashira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ijambo ngiryo riravuga, n’uwufise amatwi niyumve, uwufise amaso n’abone, kuko Uhoraho ubwiwe ni we yakenyereye ishengero ryiwe.\bd*
\pc \bdit Umve rero ncuti zanje, dusangiy’ukwizera kuzima, nimwihutire kugendera mwese, mw’ijambo ry’Imana ryose, kuko niho hari ubugingo budashira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd N’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd buntu butangaje bene\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Data, kubona Imana ariy’ikora, mbega n’impamvu yihe haba ivyo, nuko ihanga ar’iry’Imana nzima, yarikunze ritaribwabeho na gato.\bd*
\pc \bdit Umve rero ncuti zanje, dusangiy’ukwizera kuzima, nimwihutire kugendera mwese, mw’ijambo ry’Imana ryose, kuko niho hari ubugingo budashira.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Itandukanye rero n’akamenyero, mwihutire kwinjira n’ingoga, mw’ihanga ry’ukuri ry’Imana, ritari iribonwa n’amaso y’umubiri, ariko rigendera mu guhishurirwa.\bd*
\pc \bdit Umve rero ncuti zanje, dusangiy’ukwizera kuzima, nimwihutire kugendera mwese, mw’ijambo ry’Imana ryose, kuko niho hari ubugingo budashira.\bdit*
